欧洲大陆自古罗马以来便有人相食的记载，其中有因饥荒，战乱，凶杀案等复杂原因组成。

==史前==

在英国发现了有原始人同类相食的遗骸<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.britarch.ac.uk/ba/ba59/feat1.shtml |title=The edible dead |publisher=Britarch.ac.uk |access-date=August 30, 2009 |archive-date=2010-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100316144944/http://www.britarch.ac.uk/ba/ba59/feat1.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==古希腊==

古希腊神话中记载古罗诺斯吃掉自己刚出生的儿女。<ref>{{cite news |title=Cronus/cannibalism?” |url=https://ofdrabblesanddragons.wordpress.com/2017/01/20/cronuscannibalism/ |agency=OF DRABBLES AND DRAGONS |date=2020-11-16}}</ref> 

==古罗马时期==
波利比乌斯记录汉尼拔·莫诺马克斯曾建议汉尼拔·巴萨他教他的军队采取食人肉干的做法，以便在他前往意大利的旅行中得到适当的供应。<ref>Louis Rawlings, [https://www.academia.edu/3451102/_Hannibal_the_Cannibal_Polybius_on_Barcid_atrocities_Cardiff_Historical_Papers_9_Cardiff_Cardiff_School_of_History_and_Archaeology_pp._1-30 Hannibal the Cannibal? Polybius on Barcid atrocities] {{Wayback|url=https://www.academia.edu/3451102/_Hannibal_the_Cannibal_Polybius_on_Barcid_atrocities_Cardiff_Historical_Papers_9_Cardiff_Cardiff_School_of_History_and_Archaeology_pp._1-30 |date=20190815230444 }}, Cardiff Historical Papers, 2007/9</ref>

在米特拉达梯战争时期，古罗马军队在苏拉率领的部队围困雅典城时导致城中粮食缺乏，造成了严重的人相食事件。<ref>{{cite news |title=中外食人史话 |url=https://book.douban.com/subject/1028858/|accessdate=1950-10-29 |agency=豆瓣读书 |date=2020-11-16}}</ref>

罗马共和国入侵努曼西亚时期，因为战乱造成了大量人相食事件的发生。<ref>Appian. ''The Wars in Spain'', [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0230%3Atext%3DHisp.%3Achapter%3D15%3Asection%3D96 Chapter XV, Section 96] {{Wayback|url=http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0230%3Atext%3DHisp.%3Achapter%3D15%3Asection%3D96 |date=20161222031317 }}. Translated by Horace White. Hosted at the Perseus Digital Library.</ref>

弗拉维奥·约瑟夫斯围攻耶路撒冷会战中，因战乱造成城中军民大量人相食事件。<ref>Flavius Josephus. ''The Wars of the Jews'', [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0148%3Abook%3D6%3Awhiston+chapter%3D3%3Awhiston+section%3D4 Book VI, Chapter 3, Section 4] {{Wayback|url=http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0148%3Abook%3D6%3Awhiston+chapter%3D3%3Awhiston+section%3D4 |date=20161203062121 }}. Translated by William Whiston. Hosted at the Perseus Digital Library.</ref>

==中世纪时期==
第一次十字军东征时期，因战乱饥荒，当地军民与十字军都有大量人相食事件的行为。<ref>{{Cite book |author=Maalouf, Amin |title=The Crusades Through Arab Eyes |publisher=[[Schocken_Books|Schocken Books]] |location=New York |year=1984 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/crusadesthrougha00maal_0/page/37 37–40] |isbn=978-0-8052-0898-6 |url=https://archive.org/details/crusadesthrougha00maal_0/page/37 }}</ref> 

中世纪时期的欧洲也出现了用木乃伊一类的遗体入药行为<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.mummytombs.com/dummy/doctors.htm
 |title       = Medieval Doctors and Their Patients
